1. *Ponoći* sam čuo glasan zvuk automobila. (At midnight, I heard a loud sound of a car.)
2. Zašto bi neko bio budan *ponoći*? (Why would anyone be awake at midnight?)
3. U parku se često dešavaju čudne stvari *ponoći*. (Strange things often happen in the park at midnight.)
4. Moram da radim *ponoći* jer imamo rok za projekat. (I have to work at midnight because we have a deadline for the project.)
5. *Ponoći* se osećam najusamljenije. (I feel the most lonely at midnight.)
6. Počinjemo sa novim programom *ponoći* u subotu. (We're starting a new program at midnight on Saturday.)
7. Nije bezbedno šetati *ponoći* ovde. (It's not safe to walk here at midnight.)
8. Ima li neko da bi mi pravio društvo *ponoći*? (Is there anyone who would keep me company at midnight?)
9. *Ponoći* je teško naći otvorenu prodavnicu u ovom delu grada. (It's hard to find an open store in this part of the city at midnight.)
10. Molim te da ne budiš decu *ponoći*. (Please don't wake up the children at midnight.)